Arlene Martel https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arlene_Martel 0 Arlene Martel (born Arline Greta Sax, April 14, 1936 – August 12, 2014) was an American actress, writer, and acting coach. Prior to 1964, she was frequently billed as Arline Sax or Arlene Sax.
